dct_title_s: Napa, Lake County, California  : City map, including Calistoga, Clearlake Oaks, Hidden Valley Lake ... Yountville, plus American Canyon area, Clear Lake area, Cobb area (Napa, California)
dct_description_sm: Map includes street names indexes . Ancillary maps on recto: Calistoga -- St. Helena & vic. -- Lake Berryessa -- American Canyon. Inset maps on verso: Upper Lake -- Lucerne --Lake Port -- Soda Bay -- Kelseyville -- Clearlake & vicinity --Cobb and vicinity -- Hidden Valley Lake.
